{"about_the_game":"You are a journalist in search of your breakthrough story. A promising lead takes you to the abandoned island of Mythargia where you have to discover its buried history connecting two different dimensions.<br><br><i>Mythargia is a 2D side scrolling retro adventure with emphasis on discovering the island\u2019s story.</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore the island:</h2>As you search for information you will come face to face with the unnatural present on the island. Find tools and items to help you on your journey further inland. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2022470/extras/GIF-explore-the-island.gif?t=1739371219\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unravel the secrets:</h2>Leave no stone unturned as you travel deeper into the island. Solve puzzles to find all the clues you can find to get a full picture of what has happened on the island.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2022470/extras/GIF-unravel-the-secrets.gif?t=1739371219\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Discover the nightmare:</h2>Enter the other dimension and assist the islanders to earn their trust in order to learn more about them and their backgrounds.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2022470/extras/GIF-discover-the-nightmare2.gif?t=1739371219\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gather information:</h2>Write journal entries and take photos of your journey to understand what has gone down on the island of Mythargia and compile a story of the century.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2022470/extras/GIF-gather-information.gif?t=1739371219\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Starting a new journey","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2022470/65ffee0884431cdc1df26e4bd7cd73f7b6ef2633.jpg"},{"name":"Columnist","path":"ht